Discussion.S:
In these tests each antiserum showed a high degree of 
    specificity for its respective antigen (Conti et al., '87b; 
    Battaglia and Rustioni, '88; Hepler et al., '88).

This is in accordance with previous reports in other 
    corticofugal systems (Dinopoulos et al., '89, '91; 
    Giuffrida and Rustioni, '89a,b).
